{"tid":2156111,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"手足藏有雷射裝置 判監一年","createTime":"2020-08-14T08:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:45:32.000Z","uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"212727dce7ea9635ee07de815f1915218889afc6","tid":2156111,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第十三庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#0831太子 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\n<br />\n鍾(33)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：1)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n           2)無牌管有無線電通訊器具 <br />\n<br />\n於2019年8月31日在太子港鐵站內的公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，即1彈弓、48粒螺絲帽及能發出雷射光束裝置(控罪1);無牌管有無線電收發器具，即2部Motorola對講機(控罪2)<br />\n<br />\n‼️兩項控罪皆成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n控罪一判處監禁十二個月<br />\n控罪二罰款五千元，從擔保金扣除<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請上訴期間保釋被拒，上訴申請亦被拒。"},{"pid":"3e40f53dc04477a1504356ce8523c59fcbee7c95","tid":2156111,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"Onl9"},{"pid":"c7670a4348b06a9716e69a4aa6024cd6e03e2967","tid":2156111,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"3bd6f696ef5634027a58b25397ec0ca7b74b07c2","tid":2156111,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"雖然的確判得重到仆街<br />\n<br />\n但重點係佢有枝丫叉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f707a181f9cba047ab2a3df643b230bc3f5b30da","tid":2156111,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚重"},{"pid":"c8ef13d525e77a1cb660e288baac74772c130e70","tid":2156111,"uid":280648,"l